import React from "react";

const Logo = () => (
  <svg width="25%" height="25%" viewBox="0 0 500 550" version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <title>Group</title>
      <desc>Created with Sketch.</desc>
      <defs></defs>
      <g id="Page-1" stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd">
          <g id="Group-Copy" transform="translate(-6.000000, 0.000000)" fill="#FFFFFF">
              <rect id="Rectangle" x="6" y="200" width="500" height="150"></rect>
              <rect id="Rectangle" x="6" y="400" width="225" height="150"></rect>
              <rect id="Rectangle" x="281" y="400" width="225" height="150"></rect>
              <rect id="Rectangle" x="6" y="0" width="225" height="150"></rect>
              <rect id="Rectangle" x="281" y="0" width="225" height="150"></rect>
              <text id="harsimus" font-family="Helvetica-Bold, Helvetica" font-size="115" font-weight="bold">
                  <tspan x="0.338378906" y="662">harsimus</tspan>
              </text>
          </g>
      </g>
  </svg>
);

export default Logo;
